product_name: Five Ten Blackwing Climbing Shoes - Women's - 2012 Closeout
long_description: Ready for big rock adventures or sport climbing, the Five-Ten Blackwing women's climbing shoes feature sticky outsoles for great grip and a soft, wicking lining for lasting comfort. Women's-specific fit is designed for smaller feet and features a narrower heel for a snug, secure fit. Synthetic uppers offer flexible, durable comfort; padded tongues relieve pressure on tops of feet and microfiber fleece linings wick away sweat. Stealth(R) Mystique rubber outsoles grip nearly every surface and provide good edging. 2 rip-and-stick straps on the Five-Ten Blackwing women's climbing shoes provide an adjustable fit and secure closure. Closeout.
